# 🌲🔥 Forest Fire Alert Agent

**An AI-powered safety assistant that monitors simulated forest heat sensors in real-time and provides clear, friendly safety advice using OpenAI GPT-4o-mini.**

## 🎯 Overview
This project simulates a real-world IoT monitoring system where an AI agent analyzes temperature data from five distinct forest zones. It classifies conditions into four alert levels and delivers actionable safety guidance through a clean, interactive Gradio interface. Perfect for educational demos, prototyping smart city solutions, or learning how to integrate LLMs with sensor data.

## ✨ Key Features
- **Real-time Simulation**: Generates dynamic heat readings for 5 forest zones based on selected scenarios (Normal, Warning, Fire).
- **AI-Powered Analysis**: Uses **GPT-4o-mini** to interpret sensor data and answer user questions with context-aware safety advice.
- **Visual Alert System**: Color-coded alert levels (🟢 Normal, 🟡 Warning, 🟠 Danger, 🔴 Critical) for instant status recognition.
- **Secure Design**: API keys managed via `.env` files; no hardcoded secrets.
- **Interactive UI**: Built with **Gradio** for an intuitive, zero-setup user experience.

